citation: Proclamation under the Commissioner for Children and Young People Act 2016 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Commissioner for Children and Young People Act 2016

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Commissioner for Children and Young People Act 2016 fix 1 July 2016 as the day on which the provisions of that Act commence.

13 June 2016

C. WARNER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

J. PETRUSMA

Minister for Human Services

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 22 June 2016

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
